Tag comment blocks in code.
Supported symbols: `#`, `//`, `/* .. */`, `<!-- .. -->`
Derive this class to add support for other symbols.

Example:
    .. code-block :: python

        @tagger
        class CustomComments(CodeComments):
            name = "custom_comments"
            single_line_symbols = ["DEFINE HERE"]

            def tag(self, doc: Doc) -> TagResult:
                return super().tag(doc)

A singleton registry to store taggers and allow for loading of custom taggers.
Register custom taggers by deriving from DocTagger or FileTagger and using the @tagger decorator.

Example:
    .. code-block:: python

        @tagger
        class CustomTagger(DocTagger) -> TagResult:
            name = "custom_tagger"
            def predict(self, doc):
                return TagResult(doc, [])

